{"tid":1584163,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"金澤培：關站逼不得已　破壞港鐵暴力越趨嚴重","createTime":"2019-09-21T03:29:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T03:42:09.000Z","uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9b96e7b04937db3bf0917b99f2a0da3add58d102","tid":1584163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:29:47.000Z","msg":"反修例風波持續，港鐵行政總裁金澤培表示，港鐵因應風險評估而決定關站是逼不得已。<br />\n<br />\n他出席一個電台節目後被問到，是否認同主席歐陽伯權說港鐵在反修例事件初期的處理手法「難睇」，金澤培表示，自從6月以來，破壞港鐵的暴力情況越來越嚴重，是過去40年未曾遇過，因此港鐵有新的應對措施。<br />\n<br />\n至於會否參考巴黎地鐵保安人員持槍執法，考慮提升港鐵保安裝備，金澤培表示，每年都會與全球30多個鐵路系統的代表會面，其中巴黎地鐵保安持槍，同時有警察權力可以執法，屬於極端例子，他強調自己只是舉例不同地方有不同安排。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，很多地方鐵路保安的安排均與本港相似，而港鐵員工的保安工作包括票控，治安執法工作則由警方負責。"},{"pid":"307ee6254935cc0a7c778a5d62bbcd4021b7437b","tid":1584163,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481745-20190921.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481745-20190921.htm&d=ekRw3fL0jih6ME0SbOEd7%2F7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=c1bc5fbe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1481745-20190921.htm&h=c062150d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1481745-20190921.htm</a>"},{"pid":"eeac322255677f705dc6add4f3990f55456fc75b","tid":1584163,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:32:12.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">由於都係有好多人唔明行動有咩意義同目標 於是係正式攻略之前出個簡化版</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n【行動】【主線】 【922】【SUCK4.0】 【多圖】 【簡易式攻略目標 】<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1583476\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1583476</a>"},{"pid":"e507ebe5e42cc98e238c8ff1fd48fa036a1c1609","tid":1584163,"uid":25183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:33:13.000Z","msg":"建議即日起關閉所有黨鐵站<br />\n以保障黨鐵員工和物件既安全及性命<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9743d0f6a66518efe21ee3dbd9f61db80b259fa4","tid":1584163,"uid":147226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-21T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"黨鐵想成立軍隊推翻政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}